						               													<description>A 2-players card-placement micro game, only 20 cards.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Every card is consist of 6 squares, and there'll be 3 kinds activities on the card. The activities are the elements consist a life of miniversity student, which are Studying, Dating, Travelling, Part-time jobs and Hanging out with friends! You need to arrange your TIME efficiently to get better memories during all these activities.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Players each places 10 cards into their own placing zone in real time until each player has placed all their cards in their placing zone, then proceed to scoring points. The player who placed all cards faster get bonus points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Placing rule:&amp;#10;You only need to overlap the previous card you just played, at least one square. It's no matter how many squares you covered, it's also fine to overlap whole card. It's free to cover any icons, you don't have to stack the same icon in the same position.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Scoring rule:&amp;#10;In Short game, check your 3 biggest blocks, you scoring 1 point for each icon in these blocks. The faster playing get 3 bonus points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In Full game, check your biggest blocks in each kind of icon, you scoring 1 point for each icon in these blocks. Players get bonus points according to the speed rank.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
